Depends: ${misc:Depends}, ${perl:Depends}, ${shlibs:Depends}, libxml-mini-perl, libfile-find-rule-perl, libwx-perl (>= 0.93), xorg, xinit, libxml-quote-perl, libsub-override-perl
Description: super awesome keyboard and mouse testing scripts
 wxKeyboardTester and wxMouseTester are super awesome keyboard and
 mouse tester scripts used by Freegeek to test donated equipment. They
 support mouses with scroll wheels and mac or 104-key keyboards.
